To load the input, press File > Load input and
choose the desired input source and type

To adjust the animation settings, press 
File > Settings and set the animation "speed"
and the animation mode

The play button creates a new window with the animation.
It starts it with the mode set in the Settings. If the 
mode is Step-by-step, press Next button to advance 
the animation. The Stop button stops the animation
and puts the bars to their original place. The pause
button pauses the animation and sets it to Step-by-step
mode.

It is advised to keep the animation window as
'Always on top' to use the animation controls and
keep seeing the animation